DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"TO vs FC MTD"}, 'KPI1'[KPI_Name])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    TREATAS({"TMI abs Delta"}, 'KPI2'[KPI_Name])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
    TREATAS({"United Kingdom"}, 'Country Slicer'[Country])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable4 = 
    TREATAS({"GBP IN K"}, 'Exchange Rate'[Currency Code])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable5 = 
    TREATAS({"Current Month"}, 'Report'[Report])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable6 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Sub Division2])),
      NOT('Product'[Sub Division2] IN {"OTHER BEVERAGE"})
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    CALCULATETABLE(
      SUMMARIZE(
        'Company Type Slicer',
        'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type],
        'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type Sort]
      ),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable2),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable3),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable4),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable5),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable6)
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(
      1002,
      __DS0Core,
      'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type Sort],
      1,
      'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type],
      1
    )

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type Sort], 'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Category])),
      NOT(
        'Product'[Category] IN {"NON CORPORATE HC CATEGORY",
          "NON CORPORATE PC CATEGORY",
          "Royalties"}
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Customer'[Customer])),
      NOT('Customer'[Customer] IN {"Royalties"})
    )

  VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
    TREATAS({"Unilever Retail"}, 'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable4 = 
    TREATAS({"United Kingdom"}, 'Country Slicer'[Country])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable5 = 
    TREATAS({"GBP IN K"}, 'Exchange Rate'[Currency Code])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable6 = 
    TREATAS({"MTD GSV vs FC"}, 'KPI1'[KPI_Name])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable7 = 
    TREATAS({"Current Month"}, 'Report'[Report])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable8 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Sub Division2])),
      NOT('Product'[Sub Division2] IN {"OTHER BEVERAGE"})
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
        ROLLUPGROUP('Product'[Category Group], 'Product'[Category Group Seq]), "IsGrandTotalRowTotal",
        'Product'[Sub Division2], "IsDM1Total",
        ROLLUPGROUP('Product'[Category], 'Product'[Category Sort]), "IsDM3Total"
      ),
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
        ROLLUPGROUP(
          'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
          'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
          'Customer'[Account Group]
        ), "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"
      ),
      __DS0FilterTable,
      __DS0FilterTable2,
      __DS0FilterTable3,
      __DS0FilterTable4,
      __DS0FilterTable5,
      __DS0FilterTable6,
      __DS0FilterTable7,
      __DS0FilterTable8,
      "HeatMap", 'Dashboard_Measures'[HeatMap]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(
      102,
      SUMMARIZE(
        __DS0Core,
        'Product'[Category Group],
        'Product'[Category Group Seq],
        [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
        'Product'[Sub Division2],
        [IsDM1Total],
        'Product'[Category],
        'Product'[Category Sort],
        [IsDM3Total]
      ),
      [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      0,
      'Product'[Category Group Seq],
      1,
      'Product'[Category Group],
      1,
      [IsDM1Total],
      0,
      'Product'[Sub Division2],
      1,
      [IsDM3Total],
      0,
      'Product'[Category Sort],
      1,
      'Product'[Category],
      1
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(
      __DS0Core,
      'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
      'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
      [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
      'Customer'[Account Group]
    )

  VAR __DS0Secondary = 
    TOPN(
      102,
      __DS0SecondaryBase,
      [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
      1,
      'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
      1,
      'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
      1,
      'Customer'[Account Group],
      1
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __DS0PrimaryWindowed,
      SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
        __DS0Core,
        "ColumnIndex",
        __DS0Secondary,
        [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
        ASC,
        'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
        ASC,
        'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
        ASC,
        'Customer'[Account Group],
        ASC
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core),
      AND(
        AND(AND([IsGrandTotalRowTotal] = FALSE, [IsDM1Total] = FALSE), [IsDM3Total] = FALSE),
        [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE
      )
    )

EVALUATE
  GROUPBY(
    __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals,
    "MinHeatMap", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [HeatMap]),
    "MaxHeatMap", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [HeatMap])
  )

EVALUATE
  __DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
  'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
  'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
  'Customer'[Account Group]

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC,
  'Product'[Category Group Seq],
  'Product'[Category Group],
  [IsDM1Total] DESC,
  'Product'[Sub Division2],
  [IsDM3Total] DESC,
  'Product'[Category Sort],
  'Product'[Category],
  [ColumnIndex]

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(
      1002,
      __DS0Core,
      'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type Sort],
      1,
      'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type],
      1
    )

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type Sort], 'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Category])),
      NOT(
        'Product'[Category] IN {"NON CORPORATE HC CATEGORY",
          "NON CORPORATE PC CATEGORY",
          "Royalties"}
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Customer'[Customer])),
      NOT('Customer'[Customer] IN {"Royalties"})
    )

  VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
    TREATAS({"Unilever Retail"}, 'Company Type Slicer'[Company Type])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable4 = 
    TREATAS({"UK + Ireland"}, 'Country Slicer'[Country])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable5 = 
    TREATAS({"GBP IN K"}, 'Exchange Rate'[Currency Code])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable6 = 
    TREATAS({"MTD GSV vs FC"}, 'KPI1'[KPI_Name])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable7 = 
    TREATAS({"Current Month"}, 'Report'[Report])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable8 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Sub Division2])),
      NOT('Product'[Sub Division2] IN {"OTHER BEVERAGE"})
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
        ROLLUPGROUP('Product'[Category Group], 'Product'[Category Group Seq]), "IsGrandTotalRowTotal",
        'Product'[Sub Division2], "IsDM1Total",
        ROLLUPGROUP('Product'[Category], 'Product'[Category Sort]), "IsDM3Total"
      ),
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
        ROLLUPGROUP(
          'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
          'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
          'Customer'[Account Group]
        ), "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"
      ),
      __DS0FilterTable,
      __DS0FilterTable2,
      __DS0FilterTable3,
      __DS0FilterTable4,
      __DS0FilterTable5,
      __DS0FilterTable6,
      __DS0FilterTable7,
      __DS0FilterTable8,
      "HeatMap", 'Dashboard_Measures'[HeatMap]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(
      102,
      SUMMARIZE(
        __DS0Core,
        'Product'[Category Group],
        'Product'[Category Group Seq],
        [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
        'Product'[Sub Division2],
        [IsDM1Total],
        'Product'[Category],
        'Product'[Category Sort],
        [IsDM3Total]
      ),
      [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      0,
      'Product'[Category Group Seq],
      1,
      'Product'[Category Group],
      1,
      [IsDM1Total],
      0,
      'Product'[Sub Division2],
      1,
      [IsDM3Total],
      0,
      'Product'[Category Sort],
      1,
      'Product'[Category],
      1
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(
      __DS0Core,
      'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
      'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
      [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
      'Customer'[Account Group]
    )

  VAR __DS0Secondary = 
    TOPN(
      102,
      __DS0SecondaryBase,
      [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
      1,
      'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
      1,
      'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
      1,
      'Customer'[Account Group],
      1
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __DS0PrimaryWindowed,
      SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
        __DS0Core,
        "ColumnIndex",
        __DS0Secondary,
        [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
        ASC,
        'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
        ASC,
        'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
        ASC,
        'Customer'[Account Group],
        ASC
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core),
      AND(
        AND(AND([IsGrandTotalRowTotal] = FALSE, [IsDM1Total] = FALSE), [IsDM3Total] = FALSE),
        [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE
      )
    )

EVALUATE
  GROUPBY(
    __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals,
    "MinHeatMap", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [HeatMap]),
    "MaxHeatMap", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [HeatMap])
  )

EVALUATE
  __DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
  'Customer'[CustomerLevel1Desc Sort],
  'Customer'[Customer Level 1],
  'Customer'[Account Group]

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC,
  'Product'[Category Group Seq],
  'Product'[Category Group],
  [IsDM1Total] DESC,
  'Product'[Sub Division2],
  [IsDM3Total] DESC,
  'Product'[Category Sort],
  'Product'[Category],
  [ColumnIndex]

DEFINE

    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Sub Division2])),

    )

    TREATAS({"HOME CARE"}, 'Product'[Category Group])

  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'Product'[Category Sort], 'Product'[Category]

    )

  VAR __DM3FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Category Group])),
      NOT('Product'[Category Group] IN {"UNKWN"})
    )

  VAR __DM5FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(
        SUMMARIZE(VALUES('Product'), 'Product'[Category Group], 'Product'[Sub Division2])
      ),
      NOT(
        ('Product'[Category Group], 'Product'[Sub Division2]) IN {("FOOD & REFRESHMENT", "ICE CREAM"),
          ("FOOD & REFRESHMENT", "TEA")}
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
        ROLLUPGROUP('Product'[Category Group], 'Product'[Category Group Seq]), "IsGrandTotalRowTotal",
        'Product'[Sub Division2], "IsDM1Total", NONVISUAL(__DM3FilterTable),
        ROLLUPGROUP('Product'[Category], 'Product'[Category Sort]),
        "IsDM3Total",
        NONVISUAL(__DM3FilterTable),
        NONVISUAL(__DM5FilterTable)
      ),
      __DS0FilterTable,
      __DS0FilterTable2,
      __DS0FilterTable3,
      __DS0FilterTable4,
      __DS0FilterTable5,
      __DS0FilterTable6,
      "Blank_Measure", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Blank Measure],
      "TO_MTD", 'Dashboard_Measures'[TO MTD],
      "TO_MTD_vs_FC", 'Dashboard_Measures'[TO MTD vs FC],
      "Volume_MTD", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Volume MTD],
      "Volume_MTD_vs_Fc", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Volume MTD vs Fc],
      "Act_TMI_", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Act TMI%],
      "TMI__vs_FC", 'Dashboard_Measures'[TMI% vs FC],

      "TMI_abs_Delta", 'Dashboard_Measures'[TMI abs Delta],
      "Daily_Sales_rate_to_go_TO", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Daily Sales rate to go TO],
      "MTD_USG_", 'Dashboard_Measures'[MTD USG%],
      "Volume_Phased_MTD_FC", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Volume Phased MTD FC],
      "FC_MTD_TMI_", 'Dashboard_Measures'[FC MTD TMI%],
      "GSV_FC", 'Dashboard_Measures'[GSV FC],
      "Projected_GSV", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Projected GSV],
      "MTD_NIV", 'Dashboard_Measures'[MTD NIV],
      "TO_FC_MTH", 'Dashboard_Measures'[TO FC MTH],
      "Projected_TO", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Projected TO],
      "GP_MTD", 'Dashboard_Measures'[GP MTD],
      "MTD_GP_vs_FC", 'Dashboard_Measures'[MTD GP vs FC],
      "Daily_Sales_rate_to_go_GP", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Daily Sales rate to go GP],
      "GP_FC_MTH", 'Dashboard_Measures'[GP FC MTH],
      "Projected_GP", 'Dashboard_Measures'[Projected GP],
      "MTD_GP_Growth_", 'Dashboard_Measures'[MTD GP Growth%]
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM1 = 
    SELECTCOLUMNS(
      KEEPFILTERS(
        FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), AND([IsDM1Total] = TRUE, [IsDM3Total] = TRUE))
      ),
      "IsGrandTotalRowTotal", [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      "'Product'[Category Group]", 'Product'[Category Group],
      "'Product'[Category Group Seq]", 'Product'[Category Group Seq],
      "SortBy_DM1_0", [Blank_Measure]
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM3 = 
    SELECTCOLUMNS(
      KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsDM3Total] = TRUE)),
      "IsGrandTotalRowTotal", [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      "'Product'[Category Group]", 'Product'[Category Group],
      "'Product'[Category Group Seq]", 'Product'[Category Group Seq],
      "IsDM1Total", [IsDM1Total],
      "'Product'[Sub Division2]", 'Product'[Sub Division2],
      "SortBy_DM3_0", [Blank_Measure]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
        __DS0Core,
        __DS0CoreTableByDM1
      ),
      __DS0CoreTableByDM3
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(
      502,
      __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
      [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      0,
      [SortBy_DM1_0],
      0,
      'Product'[Category Group Seq],
      1,
      'Product'[Category Group],
      1,
      [IsDM1Total],
      0,
      [SortBy_DM3_0],
      0,
      'Product'[Sub Division2],
      1,
      [IsDM3Total],
      0,
      [Blank_Measure],
      0,
      'Product'[Category Sort],
      1,
      'Product'[Category],
      1
    )

  __DS0PrimaryWindowed
